### Solution 2

#### TypeScript

```ts
function toLowerCase(s: string): string {
    return [...s].map(c => String.fromCharCode(c.charCodeAt(0) | 32)).join('');
}
```

#### Rust

```rust
impl Solution {
    pub fn to_lower_case(s: String) -> String {
        s.as_bytes()
            .iter()
            .map(|&c| char::from(if c >= b'A' && c <= b'Z' { c | 32 } else { c }))
            .collect()
    }
}
```
